Vendored HID transport layer
=============================

This directory is a vendored snapshot of the HID transport layer from
HueSync (https://github.com/honjow/HueSync), licensed BSD 3-Clause
(see LICENSE). Snapshot date: 2026-06-27.

Only the HID transport pieces are vendored:
  - lib_hid/        pyhidapi ctypes wrapper (https://github.com/apmorton/pyhidapi)
  - msi_led_device_hid.py
  - legion_go_tablet_hid.py
  - legion_led_device_hid.py
  - hhd_legino_go_s_hid.py
  - utils.py        trimmed to Color + RGBMode only
  - config.py       minimal logger shim (NOT HueSync's config)

Device classes, power-LED handling, and software effects from HueSync are
NOT vendored; decky-colores supplies its own.

The Legion Go S protocol (hhd_legino_go_s_hid.py) is derived from hhd-dev/hhd
(https://github.com/hhd-dev/hhd); its provenance docstring is preserved.

